# MASTER WRITING PROMPT
## Mastering Legal Transcription — Chapter Writing Sessions

> **How to use this prompt:** Paste the entire prompt below into Claude (or your AI writing tool) at the start of each chapter writing session. Replace the `[VARIABLES]` at the bottom with the specific section you're working on.

